import math

def calculate_change(cents):
    if cents <= 0:
        cents = 0
    cents = int(cents)
    change = {}
    change['Quarters'] = cents // 25
    cents = cents % 25
    change['Dimes'] = cents // 10
    cents = cents % 10
    change['Nickels'] = cents // 5
    cents = cents % 5
    change['Pennies'] = cents
    return change
